internalGadget.documentation:
This gadget displays an activity stream for a given document
(document created / modified, like, comments, ...)

The following user preferences can be used to configure it:
- nuxeoTargetContextPath: the path of the document on which to
initialize the activity stream
- activityStreamName: the activity stream to use to retrieve the
configured list of activity verbs to get

How to include the documentactivitystream gadget in a JSF context:




    jQuery('.gadget-documentactivitystream').openSocialGadget({
      baseURL: '#{baseURL}',
      language: '#{localeSelector.language}',
      gadgetDefs: [{
        specUrl: '#{gadgetsBaseURL}/site/gadgets/documentactivitystream/documentactivitystream.xml',
        title: '',
        userPrefs: {
          nuxeoTargetContextPath: {
            value: '#{currentDocument.pathAsString}'
          },
          activityStreamName: {
            value: 'defaultDocumentActivityStream'
          }
        },
        displayTitleBar: false,
        width: '100%'
      }]
    });



How to include the documentactivitystream gadget in a WebEngine page:








    $('.gadget-documentactivitystream').openSocialGadget({
      baseURL: '${contextPath}' + '/',
      language: '${Context.locale.language}',
      gadgetDefs: [{
        specUrl : '${Runtime.getProperty('nuxeo.loopback.url')}/site/gadgets/documentactivitystream/documentactivitystream.xml',
        userPrefs: {
          nuxeoTargetContextPath: {
            value: '${doc.pathAsString}'
          },
          activityStreamName: {
            value: 'defaultDocumentActivityStream'
          }
        },
        displayTitleBar: false,
        width: '100%'
      }]
    });
